			(table_cell "Swapped DDR bits D1/D4 and D2/D7; Delete DDR TPs for GND and VREF\nChanged USB ESD diodes D3 from SP0503BAHTG to USBLC6-2SC6\nAdded C150 and F19 at P5V_DEGUB_VBUS\nRemoved R255 pull-up on ENET1_INT, redundant\nRemoved test points for ENET2 unused pins\nAdded fiducials FID1 to FID6, Tooling Holes H5 to H7\nOn eMMC, connected NC pins to nets for ease of routing\nPCBA Revision 1 prototype build"
